junit.framework.Test
public class UD_Unsubscribe_EditionsPerks
extends iTestCaseUD

This test series creates an UD account, signs up for perks and editorials, and then logs out. It the next test logs in again with the same account and unchecks all the perks the account signed up with; effectively unsubscribing the account from all email.
